description:
https://twitter.com/RealTamers12345
I figured it was about time I spread Sonic Underground in more ways than just youtube. Like on twitter... Twitter because I've been I'm IP banned on Deviantart because the mods there hate my art LOL

Don't be afraid to hit me up on there so we can talk about how much you like me and Sonic underground and shit.
https://twitter.com/RealTamers12345

comments.text: Why does your Twitter page say that you've been on the site since 2011?
comments.author: Canas

comments.text:
I can never tell if tamers is a troll, legit believes his delusions, or is just a passionate fan of Underground who takes things to far.

I myself, like Sonic Underground, I think it's underrated, and would love it see it come back, but I don't think I'd ever take things this far. sure, I ship characters, want it to return, and enjoy the show, but tamers is well... "a bit off" to put it lightly. I'm fine with him being a fan, hell, I think SU needs more fans, but to this extreme? I'm not sure.

in any case, Tamers, keep doing what your doing! it's entertaining as hell! XD
comments.author: TheIronJedi
